quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  19,12,ae yahya ( hamari ) kitaab ko zor se pakdae raho. aur hum ne un ko larakpan mein danai ataa farmai thi
  19,13,aur apne paas shafqat aur pakizgee di thi. aur parhaizgaar they
  19,14,aur maa baap ke sath neki karne walay they aur sarkash aur nafarman nahi they
  19,15,aur jis din woh peda hue aur jis din wafaat payen ge aur jis din zindah karkay uthaye jayen ge. un par salam aur rehmat ( hai )
  19,16,"aur kitaab ( quran ) mein maryam ka bhi mazkoor karo, jab woh apne logon se allag ho kar mashriq ki taraf chali gayeen"
  19,17,to unhon ne un ki taraf se parda karliya. ( is waqt ) hum ne un ki taraf apna farishta bheja. to un ke samnay theek aadmi ( ki shakal ) ban gaya
  19,18,maryam bolein ke agar tum parhaizgaar ho to mein tum se khuda ki panah maangti hon
  19,19,unhon ne kaha ke mein to tumahray perwar-digaar ka bheja howa ( yani farishta ) hon ( aur is liye aaya hon ) ke tumhe pakeeza larka bakhson
  19,20,maryam ne kaha ke mere haan larka kyonkr hoga mujhe kisi bashar ne chuva taq nahi aur mein badkaar bhi nahi hon
  19,21,( farishtay ne ) kaha ke yuhin ( hoga ) tumahray perwar-digaar ne farmaya ke yeh mujhe aasaan hai. aur ( mein usay isi tareeq par peda karoon ga ) taakay is ko logon ke liye apni taraf se nishani aurzarya rehmat aur ( meharbani ) bunun aur yeh kaam muqarrar hochuka hai
  19,22,to woh is ( bachay ) ke sath haamla hogyin aur usay le kar aik daur jagah chali gayeen
  19,23,phir dard zeh un ko khajoor ke tanay ki taraf le aaya. kehnay lagen ke kash mein is se pehlay mar chukti aur bholi bisri ho gayi hoti
  19,24,is waqt un ke neechay ki janib se farishtay ne un ko aawaz di ke ghumnaak nah ho tumahray perwar-digaar ne tumahray neechay aik chashma jari kardiya hai
  19,25,aur khajoor ke tanay ko pakar kar apni taraf hilaoo tum par taaza taaza khjorin jhar parrin gi
